<detall><id label=""><![CDATA[78789]]></id><title label="Titol"><![CDATA[Sign up for the 'correfocs' at the Festa Major in Sants!]]></title><excerpt label="Resum"><![CDATA[<strong>Festivals.</strong> This Saturday evening the neighbourhood streets will be full of sparks and drums.]]></excerpt><content label="Contingut"><![CDATA[<p>The afternoon and evening of Saturday 30 August is clearly aimed at getting young and old to enjoy an activity strongly rooted in Catalonia&#8217;s folk culture. What&#8217;s more, at the Festa Major in Sants there will be correfocs for everyone. First, one for young children late in the afternoon, with three colles de diables, or devil groups, taking part.</p>
<p>Later, in the evening, it will be the turn of the adults, when another three groups will have the job of livening up the festival and showering themselves and onlookers with sparks, to the rhythm of the drums and the music. It is important everyone who wants to have a good time does so, but without running any risks and showing the awareness demanded by a correfoc, literally a &#8220;fire run&#8221;.when the firework-totting devils dance their way round the streets. As they will on Saturday evening, when the streets of Sants will be alive with music and alight with sparks as the neighbourhood celebrates its big festival, the festa major.</p>
